      "content": "i know it's not ideal but i'm just so exhausted and i really need to sleep. it was just one small glass though, not like i'm drunk or anything. surely a little bit of wine wont make a huge difference or make me stop breathing? it feels like it would just help me relax more so i can actually fall asleep.",
